Package: CactusPhylo
Type: Package
Title: Phylogenetic Inference and Divergence Time Estimation Pipeline for Cactaceae
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Beatriz M. Meriño <b.vergara.m@gmail.com> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Beatriz M. Meriño <b.vergara.m@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a reproducible workflow for reconstructing Cactaceae phylogenies from DNA sequence data. The pipeline automates GenBank sequence  retrieval, multiple-sequence alignment, substitution model selection, saturation assessment, supermatrix construction, maximum-likelihood phylogenetic inference using RAxML-NG, divergence time estimation with treePL, and tree-space analyses for assessing phylogenetic stability across bootstrap replicates.
URL: https://github.com/beeamerino/CactusPhylo, https://beeamerino.github.io/CactusPhylo, https://beeamerino.github.io/CactusPhylo/
